Dakar.title: Dakar
Dakar.byline: Dakar is the capital and largest city of Senegal and is often regarded as the cultural and commercial center of French-speaking West Africa.

Dakhla Oasis.title: Dakhla Oasis
Dakhla Oasis.byline: Dakhla (Arabic الداخلة) is an oasis in the Western Desert of Egypt, 740 km from Cairo.

Dakshina Kannada.title: Dakshina Kannada
Dakshina Kannada.byline: Dakshina Kannada or South Canara is a district in the Karavali region of Karnataka.

Dakshin Dinajpur.title: Dakshin Dinajpur
Dakshin Dinajpur.byline: Dakshin Dinajpur is a district of West Bengal, India.
